<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showMessageRange?topicID=6903.topic&amp;start=51&amp;stop=51">Eandori: Well I'm a mage, and I have root</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
