<br>
You keep arguing that root will overpower us...no, not arguing, just saying it. Arguing amount to actually showing arguments. You say you don't have to prove that root would over power us, I disagree. If there was irefutable proof then I'm sure all of us asking for it or other form of defense will shut up and never mention it again.<br>
<br>
About the necro pets. I did mention that the lv 50+ are different because they are situational (monk pet, rogue pet)but the ones below 50 are very close to ours. It is like comparing our 50+ fire pet and earth pet, of course earth one tanks better. Checking the new necro pets for PoP it seems they are getting a new warrior pet too, will that one be close in tanking to ours? (and I don't consider epic pet valid for the equation). I don't know why they didnt' get a warrior pet 50+ since they surelly needed one too.  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ukardazashgate.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kardaz Ashgate</A> at: 10/5/02 1:58:54 am<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showMessageRange?topicID=375.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showMessageRange?topicID=375.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showMessageRange?topicID=375.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a> <b>4</b> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showMessageRange?topicID=375.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showMessageRange?topicID=375.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showMessageRange?topicID=375.topic&start=121&stop=140>7</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showMessageRange?topicID=375.topic&start=141&stop=160>8</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showMessageRange?topicID=375.topic&start=161&stop=180>9</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showMessageRange?topicID=375.topic&start=181&stop=200>10</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showMessageRange?topicID=375.topic&start=201&stop=202>11</a> </td><td align=rig